{"tid":1723480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母米撚再守大學","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:31:31.000Z","uid":235644,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"289e2046dca2f7a78650f0d985a8ac7c9cb90f9e","tid":1723480,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"你地訓撚醒未？<br />\n<br />\n佔中話我地知，只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">轉攻為守就會輸</span></strong></span>，一來狗已經有齊裝備，硬撼一定令手足傷到仆街，二來政府係佔中後亦都有晒經驗清場，三就係好容易比啲分化撚搵位入。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家打返<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊擊</span></span></strong>，好好諗清楚每次行動有乜<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重要目標</span></strong></span>，目標完成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好戀戰即刻退</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n唔想見到場杖會輸，亦都唔想見到咁多位手足流血有事！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>做好主線：<br />\n1. 不合作運動<br />\n2. 對準一切同政府有關單位<br />\n3. 黃色經濟圈</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5860723ac9bf2c429ac0db4f6e8cee54278f4f64","tid":1723480,"uid":13412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"1d1cb4cbbae15ba1462758e3ebf54096d94ca02b","tid":1723480,"uid":289160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefb744acf94e206b54fd9c3b79692ba17321272","tid":1723480,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇語氣就知5毛 blocked"},{"pid":"d38da8817c7181a8a63da3dc7fd16a31d1ad31d9","tid":1723480,"uid":102529,"like":0,"dislike